title: Science Report - Alternative 3 - Moon Mars Conspiracy
description:
This is a 1977 British "Gotcha-mentary" about missing persons, NASA cover-ups, and the moon landings conspiracy.

No, not the conventional moon landing conspiracy.  Bart Sibrel couldn't pour water out of a boot if you wrote instructions on the heel.

This one is even sillier, and puts the tongue in the opposite cheek.  It proposes that missing scientists and other notables are being sent to the Moon and Mars because another ice is coming and the Earth is doomed
